# Anti-Spam Discord Bot

A Discord.js v14 bot that automatically bans suspicious users based on username patterns and account age, and logs the actions to a channel.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Auto-ban users with suspicious usernames (e.g. `token`, `john f`, `motion`, `tokens.rip`)
- Auto-ban accounts less than 1 minute old
- Deletes 7 days of messages on ban
- Logs bans in a specified log channel
- Custom presence: "Listening to idiots"

---

## 🧰 Requirements

- Node.js v18+
- Visual Studio Code
- Discord bot token
- Log channel ID from your server

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sreemanrp/Auto-Banner.git
cd auto-banner
